summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, governing the location of adult cabarets and providing for termination of nonconforming adult cabaret uses, amending sections 23.47.004, 23.49.062, 23.49.118, 23.49.144, 23.49.320, 23.49.388, 23.50.012, 23.66.122, 23.66.322, 23.84.006, 23.84.030 of the Seattle Municipal (Land Use) Code and adding Section 23.49.027 to the Seattle Municipal (Land Use) Code.
